CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 20, 1962, pg. 1 reads:"President Kennedy Stumps Area for Democrats - Aliquippa's Welcome on Friday found thousands of persons on the hillsides and throughout the town's areas."
TitMainTitle: Crowd on hillside and in street for President John F. Kennedy visit, with political signs for William Kovolenko for Legislative Representative and "Let's Free the Toll Bridge," Aliquippa
